T02TD1596E:114b-1: dzny'a na a'a be sha bi dhi:/
T02TD1596E:114b-3: ye shes dbab pa'i cho ga / rdo rje rnal 'byor ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1596E:114b-4: lhan cig skyes pa bdag nyid mchog / rdo rje phag mo dpal btud nas //
T02TD1596E:114b-5: de tshe yid ches byed pa yi //
T02TD1596E:114b-6: ye shes dbab pa'i cho ga bshad //
T02TD1596E:114b-7: dri dang me tog brgyan pa yi //
T02TD1596E:114b-8: dben pa'i phyogs su bzhugs nas su //
T02TD1596E:114b-9: gnas bdag rnal 'byor bsrung don du //
T02TD1596E:114b-10: h'um phat brjod par bya ba yin //
T02TD1596E:114b-11: de nas sngags pa mnyam gzhag nas //
T02TD1596E:114b-12: bde ba'i stan la 'dug nas ni //
T02TD1596E:114b-13: lha mo'i sngags kyi cho ga bzhin //
T02TD1596E:114b-14: go cha yan lag la dgod bya //
T02TD1596E:114b-15: rtse mo brgyad pa dbab bya ste //
T02TD1596E:114b-16: mdun du dkyil 'khor dmar po ni //
T02TD1596E:114b-17: me tog dmar po dang ldan pas //
T02TD1596E:114b-18: dag pa'i gsang sngags brjod par bya //
T02TD1596E:114b-19: de nas glang po che yi rgyab //
T02TD1596E:114b-20: 'khar ba'i snod mnyam pa'i ngos la //
T02TD1596E:114b-21: lha mo'i sngags mchog dam pa yi //
T02TD1596E:114b-22: lag pa g-yon pas bri bar bya //
T02TD1596E:114b-23: de la khar la sogs sngags //
T02TD1596E:114b-24: lha mo rnams phyogs man ngag bzhin //
T02TD1596E:114b-25: dbus su rdo rje rnal 'byor ma //
T02TD1596E:114b-26: thod pa'i nang du legs par bri //
T02TD1596E:114b-27: sngags kyi phyi rol g-yung drung ngam //
T02TD1596E:114b-28: sna tshogs rdo rjes bskor bar bya //
T02TD1596E:114b-29: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i steng du ni //
T02TD1596E:114b-30: sngar bshad snod ni gsal bar bzhag / mchod yon sogs phul blo bzang gis //
T02TD1596E:114b-32: lha mo'i 'khor lo bkug nas su //
T02TD1596E:114b-33: bcug ste bcing zhing dge bar bya //
T02TD1596E:114b-34: de nas bdud rtsi dang sgron ma //
T02TD1596E:114b-35: 'dod pa'i yon tan dang bcas pa'i //
T02TD1596E:114b-36: mchod pa lnga yis rnam kun tu //
T02TD1596E:114b-37: lha mo 'khor lo mchod par bya //
T02TD1596E:114b-38: nyin re'am thun mtshams so so la //
T02TD1596E:114b-39: ji skad bshad pa'i mchod pa bya //
T02TD1596E:114b-40: de ltar ma lcogs kyang mar ngo'i //
T02TD1596E:114b-41: tshes bcu 'khor lo rtag tu mchod //
T02TD1596E:114b-42: legs par bris pa'i gsang sngags ni //
T02TD1596E:114b-43: mnyam gzhag rdo rje tshig gis bzlas //
T02TD1596E:114b-45: cho ga bzang pos bstod par bya //
T02TD1596E:114b-46: 'di ni phyi rol dag gsang ba'i mchod pa'i cho ga'o /
T02TD1596E:114b-48: // / sprul pa'i shing rta'i yan lag la //
T02TD1596E:114b-49: srog bral brang steng gtum 'od can //
T02TD1596E:115a-1: pag gdong snying rje'i bdag / kang ke li king shu ka'i 'od //
T02TD1596E:115a-3: rdo rjes brgyus pa'i thod phreng gis //
T02TD1596E:115a-4: mgor bcings khrag 'dzag mgo phreng brgyan //
T02TD1596E:115a-5: phyag g-yas gri gug bsnams pa ste //
T02TD1596E:115a-6: sdig sgrib ma lus 'joms par byed ;
T02TD1596E:115a-7: / khrag gis bkang ba'i thod pa ni //
T02TD1596E:115a-8: g-yon pa'i phyag na 'dzin par mdzad //
T02TD1596E:115a-9: phyogs kyi gos can dga' chen po //
T02TD1596E:115a-10: lus bzang bcu drug lo lon pa //
T02TD1596E:115a-11: spyan gsum mgo skyes grol ba 'phyang //
T02TD1596E:115a-12: skyil krung phyed pa'i gar dang ldan //
T02TD1596E:115a-13: sgeg pa la sogs ror bcas pa ;
T02TD1596E:115a-14: / phyag rgya lnga yis rnam par brgyan //
T02TD1596E:115a-15: phyogs rnams kun tu mkha' 'gro ma //
T02TD1596E:115a-16: tshogs 'phro ba yi gang ba yis //
T02TD1596E:115a-17: rdo rje phag mo bsgom par bya //
T02TD1596E:115a-18: ye shes bkug ste der bcug nas //
T02TD1596E:115a-19: bcings te dgyes par byas nas su //
T02TD1596E:115a-20: mkhas pas yid las byung ba yi ;
T02TD1596E:115a-21: / mchod pa de la cho ga bzhin //
T02TD1596E:115a-22: mchod pa bya ste de nas yang //
T02TD1596E:115a-23: de yi nu ma'i bar du ni //
T02TD1596E:115a-24: chu skyes byu ru lta bu yi //
T02TD1596E:115a-25: kha phye rgyas par gyur pa ni //
T02TD1596E:115a-26: rang bzhin med pa bdag med mchog / mdzes dga' skyes par byed pa'o //
T02TD1596E:115a-27: thur ltas ro chen po dang ldan//
T02TD1596E:115a-28: 'od zer gsal bas bskor ba ni //
T02TD1596E:115a-29: sna rtser mig gtad bsgom par bya //
T02TD1596E:115a-30: sa yis phur pa'i gnyen po ni //
T02TD1596E:115a-31: sprul par me tog dmar po la //
T02TD1596E:115a-33: myur du 'khor bar bsgom par bya //
T02TD1596E:115a-34: de nas sngar bshad de de yi //
T02TD1596E:115a-36: bsgoms te bsgoms pa'i bdag nyid can //
T02TD1596E:115a-37: bde ba'i rgyun du nub bltas te //
T02TD1596E:115a-38: de ltar rtag tu sgom byed pas //
T02TD1596E:115a-39: mgon po dang bcas bdag nyid che //
T02TD1596E:115a-40: phyag rgya chen po'i dngos grub ni //
T02TD1596E:115a-42: ldang bar 'dod na mkhar gnas pa'i //
T02TD1596E:115a-43: bla ma lha mor phyag 'tshal nas //
T02TD1596E:115a-44: mu:zhes brjod de langs nas su //
T02TD1596E:115a-45: cho ga de nyid rig pas bya //
T02TD1596E:115a-48: // / mandala bris ma byed pa yi //
T02TD1596E:115a-49: slob mas gsol btab bsngags pa'i sa //
T02TD1596E:115a-50: cho ga tshang bar tshes bcu'i tshe //
T02TD1596E:115b-0: de dag rjes su @115b gzung bar bya //
T02TD1596E:115b-2: mchod pa cho ga bzhin mchod cing //
T02TD1596E:115b-3: sngar bstan rnal 'byor mchog byas nas //
T02TD1596E:115b-4: slob ma'i drung du 'gro bar bya //
T02TD1596E:115b-5: mandala byed pa'i slob ma ni //
T02TD1596E:115b-6: yon phul 'greng ste gnas nas su //
T02TD1596E:115b-7: me tog phreng ba 'dzin pa la //
T02TD1596E:115b-8: mgon po can gyis blta bar bya //
T02TD1596E:115b-9: de nas ji skad gsungs pa bzhin //
T02TD1596E:115b-10: slob ma bzhi yi 'khor lor bsam //
T02TD1596E:115b-11: me tog chang dang bcas pa yis //
T02TD1596E:115b-12: lha mo yang dang yang du mchod //
T02TD1596E:115b-13: lha mo'i gsang sngags bzlas nas su //
T02TD1596E:115b-14: lag pa spos thogs brdeg par bya //
T02TD1596E:115b-15: tshangs pa'i dang po la sogs can ;
T02TD1596E:115b-16: / bden pa lan gsum brjod pa'i mthar //
T02TD1596E:115b-17: ri dgra gri gug gdon par bya //
T02TD1596E:115b-18: ltung byed mo yi chung ma ni //
T02TD1596E:115b-19: phyis nas rim pa bzhin du bzlas //
T02TD1596E:115b-20: ji srid babs par ma gyur par //
T02TD1596E:115b-21: sngags de dag ni bsgom par bya //
T02TD1596E:115b-22: ye shes babs nas slob ma ni //
T02TD1596E:115b-24: gal te cho ga bzhin bris nas //
T02TD1596E:115b-25: dge mi dge des ston par 'gyur //
T02TD1596E:115b-26: rang gi rang bzhin du gnas na //
T02TD1596E:115b-27: de nas bsgom par bstan par bya //
T02TD1596E:115b-28: lha mo'i sngags dang mchod pa dang //
T02TD1596E:115b-29: lhan cig skyes bdag de nyid bshad //
T02TD1596E:115b-30: blo bzang ye shes babs pa yis //
T02TD1596E:115b-31: de yi mdo la yid ches pa //
T02TD1596E:115b-32: de la bstan gyis gus dman pa'i //
T02TD1596E:115b-33: slob ma la ni nam yang min //
T02TD1596E:115b-34: 'di ni slob ma rjes su gzung ba'i cho ga'o /
T02TD1596E:115b-36: // / lha mo gang gis bris pa dang //
T02TD1596E:115b-37: cho ga bzhin du de yi sngags //
T02TD1596E:115b-38: bris pa de yis nus pa kun //
T02TD1596E:115b-39: kun nas gdon las bzlog pa yin //
T02TD1596E:115b-40: ye shes dbab pa'i cho ga 'dis //
T02TD1596E:115b-41: yid ches rang gis yang dag mthong //
T02TD1596E:115b-42: nyes pa thams cad 'joms byed pa //
T02TD1596E:115b-44: ye shes dbab pa'i cho ga 'bad pa yis //
T02TD1596E:115b-45: bdag gis las byas skyes pa'i dge ba gang //
T02TD1596E:115b-46: de yis myur du yang dag ye shes can //
T02TD1596E:115b-47: bde gshegs 'gro ba rnams kyis thob par shog / ye shes dbab pa'i cho ga rdzogs so /
